<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 12:29:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Kalshi 获得向专业人士提供保证金交易的许可</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-27/kalshi-approved-for-margin-trading-as-it-lures-wall-street-pros</link><description>Kalshi Inc. 已获得许可证，允许其向用户提供保证金交易，这一功能将使预测市场平台对成熟的机构投资者更具吸引力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i9bau6RgdjV8/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 18:33:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-27/kalshi-approved-for-margin-trading-as-it-lures-wall-street-pros</guid></item><item><title>随着期权指向更深层次的下跌，比特币继续下滑</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-27/bitcoin-slumps-with-options-showing-traders-turning-defensive</link><description>由于今年最大的期权到期后交易者转向防御，而投资者继续从加密货币交易所交易基金中撤资，比特币跌至三周多以来的最低水平。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iqBaYVLFGHv4/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 11:43:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-27/bitcoin-slumps-with-options-showing-traders-turning-defensive</guid></item><item><title>加密货币交易者正在转变为大型跨资产追逐者</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-24/crypto-perps-platforms-are-increasingly-used-for-trading-tradfi-assets</link><description>Hyperliquid、Ostium 等网站发现传统资产永续资产占据了更大的交易量份额&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iViar1s5soj4/v9/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-24/crypto-perps-platforms-are-increasingly-used-for-trading-tradfi-assets</guid></item><item><title>参议员询问比特大陆相关的“国家安全担忧”</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-27/senator-asks-about-bitmain-related-national-security-concerns</link><description>彭博新闻社去年 11 月报道称，一家中国比特币挖矿制造商已成为联邦调查的焦点，之后，一名民主党参议员向美国商务部索要有关如何解决该公司所造成的“潜在国家安全问题”的信息。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iBrixsrWLeqk/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 16:16:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-27/senator-asks-about-bitmain-related-national-security-concerns</guid></item></channel></rss>